title: Hour 1 - Broncos Booed at Home, Mike Klis
itunes:title: Hour 1 - Broncos Booed at Home, Mike Klis
description:
Dan reacts to last night's awful football game where the Indianapolis Colts squeaked by the Denver Broncos in overtime and zero touchdowns were scored. And Broncos Insider Mike Klis stops in and talks about how the fanbase is feeling about their new QB, Russell Wilson.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
